{"id":681790,"title":"06｜目标的描述要遵循SMART原则","content":"","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":379429,"user_name":"进化菌","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1276861,"ip_address":"广东","ucode":"B30A5F78BB4171","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/7b/bd/ccb37425.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1691937210,"is_pvip":true,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":4,"score":2,"product_id":100610401,"comment_content":"我要找一个好工作，不是目标，那是你的想法。\n\n目标的描述遵循SMART原则。什么是SMART原则呢？\nSpecific 明确性（量化的指标或明确的行为），比如“好工作”中是指薪水、工作环境、晋升机会、工作时间、公司文化或其他哪些方面？\nMeasurable 可衡量性，比如“好工作”中你期待每周工作多少小时？\nAchievable 可实现性，比如“好工作”中，根据你的经验和技能，你能达到上述的要求吗？\nRelevant 相关性（资源或限制条件），比如“好工作”中根据你的经验和技能，你能达到上述的要求吗？\nTime-Bound 时限性，比如“好工作”中你希望在什么时候找到这份工作？","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":379013,"user_name":"郭嵩阳","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1080998,"ip_address":"北京","ucode":"9DC42C7B73F580","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/7e/a6/188817b6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1691137158,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100610401,"comment_content":"这么好的课程学习人这么少,极客要好好的推进一下啊","like_count":0}]}